'''庫爾德語語法'''（{{lang-en|Kurdish grammar}}、庫德語語法、rêzimana kurdî、ڕێزمانی کوردی）為[[庫爾德語|庫爾德語]]之[[語法|語法]]，庫爾德語是一種[[屈折語|屈折語]]，它增加了[[前綴|前綴]]和[[後綴|後綴]]的至[[词根|词根]]來表示語詞之語法關係，並形成文字形式。

== 作格語言特徵 ==
在所有[[伊朗语支|伊朗语支]]裡，只有[[亞爾挪比語|亞爾挪比語]]及庫爾德語為[[作通格語言|作格語言]]，語法均含有「格位標記」（case-marking）和「動詞一致」（verb-agreement）這兩方面的特性。<ref>John R. Payne,"Ergative Construction"[http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/ergative-construction] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/ergative-construction |date=20211216181515 }},Encyclopaedia Iranica Vol. VIII, Fasc. 5, pp. 555-558,January 19, 2012.</ref> 庫爾德語裡對於作格有一般性的表述，<ref>vorgelegt von
Geoﬀrey L. J. Haig,"Alignment in Kurdish:a diachronic perspective"[http://kurdishacademy.org/sites/default/files/KurdAlignment_0.pdf] {{Wayback|url=http://kurdishacademy.org/sites/default/files/KurdAlignment_0.pdf |date=20130129135720 }},Christian-Albrechts-Universit¨,Juni 2004.</ref><ref>Theodora Bynon. 1979. The Ergative Construction in Kurdish. ''Bulletin of the School of Oriental and African Studies'' Vol. 42, No. 2, pp. 211-224.
</ref> 同樣的對於作格的特殊性也有所表述，比如在「索拉尼庫爾德語」（Sorani）<ref>John Haiman. Ergativity in Sorani Kurdish. ''Essais de typologie et de linguistique générale : mélanges offerts à Denis Creissels''. Ed. Franck Florici et al. Lyon: ENS Editions, 2010. 243-250</ref> 和「拉丁庫曼希庫爾德語」（Kurmanjî）的使用上。<ref>Geoffrey Haig,"Grammatical Relations In Kurdic Languages: A Diachronic Perspective"[http://www.ling.helsinki.fi/uhlcs/LENCA/LENCA-2/information/datei/14-haig.pdf Abstract on origins of ergativity] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ling.helsinki.fi/uhlcs/LENCA/LENCA-2/information/datei/14-haig.pdf |date=20160304052711 }},Universität Kiel,retrieved 2014.</ref>

